Definition: genus of deciduous and evergreen east Asian trees and shrubs widely cultivated as ornamentals for their white flowers and red fruits
Example: in some classifications includes genus Heteromeles
Synonyms: genus_Photinia, rosid_dicot_genus, family_Rosaceae, m, genus, of, deciduous, and, evergreen, east, Asian, trees, shrubs, widely, cultivated, as, ornamentals, for, their, white, flowers, red, fruits, in, some, classifications, includes, Heteromeles
Category: noun.plant
